cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving the accuracy of inverse dynamics models for robots using machine learning techniques. The focus is on collaborative human-robot interaction, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning (cs.LG) and feedback control (cs.SY) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of task-specific models (cs.AI) and simulation (cs.CV) to analyze the effectiveness of the proposed method.
